Class AVList

  • java.lang.Object
    • Concepts.AVObject
      • Concepts.AVList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AVList
extends AVObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents lists of attribute values. Each attribute value is a constrained or unconstrained singleton attribute value.
